<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
        <img src="/images/clinic.jpg" alt="Snuggly Bubbly Paws Banner" class="img-fluid mt-3">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="mt-5">About Snuggly Bubbly Paws</h2>
            <p>
                At Snuggly Bubbly Paws, we believe that every pet deserves exceptional care, compassion, and a lifetime
                of good health. Our dedicated team of veterinarians and veterinary nurses is committed to providing
                high-quality medical care in a safe, welcoming, and stress-free environment for both pets and their
                owners.
                <br><br>
                We offer a comprehensive range of veterinary services, including routine health check-ups, vaccinations,
                diagnostics, surgery, dental care, and preventive treatments. Using modern equipment and best veterinary
                practices, we strive to ensure every pet receives the personalized care they deserve.
                <br><br>
                Beyond medical treatment, we believe that educating pet owners is just as important. After every
                consultation, our team provides personalized recommendations and home care advice to help owners
                continue supporting their pet's recovery and overall wellbeing. By working together with pet owners, we
                aim to give every furry companion the opportunity to live a healthier, happier, and purrfect life.
                <br><br>
                Whether you're visiting us for your pet's first health check or ongoing medical care, Snuggly Bubbly
                Paws is here to support you every step of the way with professionalism, compassion, and genuine love for
                animals.

            </p>
        </div>
</body>

